message.content:
Enkosi ngokundithengisa ngokuthi ndingumfanekiso kwi-software okanye inkqubo yokusebenza. Ndingakunceda ngokuba ndibhekise ukuthi ufumana ukufaneleka ngokwenene. Ndiza kukunceda kunye nezinto ezi:

1. Ukufaka upaphelele kwakho:
   - Hlela ikhompyutha yakho.
   - Funa ikhasi lewebhusayithi ye-software okanye inkqubo yokusebenza oyifumana.
   - Hlela ukhasi lokufaka upaphelele.
   - Beka umgomo wokufaka upaphelele kwakho kwi-xhosa.
   - Beka iindlela zokuzalisa upaphelele, ukukhokela upaphelele, nokwenza iwathengise.
   - Qhagamshelana neminqweno emibili ngokusebenzisa iindlela zakho zokugqibela.

2. Ukufaka amaqaphelo:
   - Hlela ikhompyutha yakho.
   - Funa ikhasi lewebhusayithi ye-software okanye inkqubo yokusebenza oyifumana.
   - Hlela ukhasi lokufaka amaqaphelo.
   - Beka umgomo wokufaka amaqaphelo kwakho kwi-xhosa.
   - Beka iindlela zokuzalisa amaqaphelo, ukukhokela amaqaphelo, nokwenza iwathengise.
   - Qhagamshelana neminqweno emibili ngokusebenzisa iindlela zakho zokugqibela.

3. Ukufaka iintsalelo:
   - Hlela ikhompyutha yakho.
   - Funa ikhasi lewebhusayithi ye-software okanye inkqubo yokusebenza oyifumana.
   - Hlela ukhasi lokufaka iintsalelo.
   - Beka umgomo wokufaka iintsalelo kwakho kwi-xhosa.
   - B
